<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #1976d2; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; background: #f5f5f5; }
    .item { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; }
    .total { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #1976d2; text-align: right; margin-top: 20px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #1976d2; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 20px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Orcamento</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Ola <strong>{{clienteNome}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>Segue o orcamento para o veiculo <strong>{{veiculoModelo}}</strong> - Placa <strong>{{veiculoPlaca}}</strong>:</p>

      <h3>Servicos:</h3>
      {{#each itens}}
      <div class="item">
        <span>{{nome}}</span>
        <span>R$ {{valor}}</span>
      </div>
      {{/each}}

      <div class="total">Total: R$ {{valorTotal}}</div>

      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{portalLink}}" class="button">Ver Orcamento e Aprovar</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Este e um email automatico. Nao responda.</p>
      <p>Auto OS</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
